==English==

===Noun===
'''[[transitive]] [[verb]]'''

#{{grammar}}: A verb that is accompanied (either clearly or implicitly) by a direct object in active sentences. It links the action taken by the subject with the object upon which that action is taken.  Consequently, it may be used in a passive voice.

